Akken i t-yewweḍ lameṛ-agi, aɛessas-nni yerra-ten ɣer lḥebs yellan seddaw tmurt, yerna yurez-asen idaṛṛen s snasel.
Di mkul amkan n tmurt i d-yețwaɛfan i iyunaniyen iḍuɛen Sidi Ṛebbi. Iɛekkumt-ed iman-nsen di ddnubat-nsen, iwakken a d-yekker wid i ten-ițqehhiṛen ula d nutni.
?-țameddit n wass i deg țheggin iman-nsen i wass n westeɛfu, daymi a d-yas lweqt i deg ara sen-d-isbeggen iman-nsen d wamek ara t-ildin abrid. ?-țedṛu d umeslay i deg tecɛelli n tafat n Sidi Ṛebbi armi d ass i deg yețwarfed ɣer igenni.
Ma d win yețdumun, ur yuḥwaǧ ara a d-yeǧǧ lxedma-s n uḥeǧǧaǧu n tmes n walebɛaḍ, isem-is n nnbi Iceɛya i gesbedd deg-s.
Tajmaɛt-nni n tmes i d-yegran ɣef yixef n wedrar izerman, yiwen umezlen azeggaɣ ɣlayen si mkul tama.
Ɣef wayagi, mazal-ikkun teṭṭfeḍ, ilaq a kkun-id-yaweḍ lxiṛ-agi ɣer tmezduɣt, dinna ara theggim imensi n Tfaska.
D ayen ur nezmir ara a t-tnekkeṛ ɣef kra n wayen yellan deg igenwan ; acḥal i gzemren a t-selken si lexṣaṣ, neɣ m'ulac a t-selken si lexṣaṣ n ddunit meṛṛa ;
Xemmemet ihi ɣuṛ-es aț-țwalim amek i geqbel leɛtab n yemdanen iweɛṛen n tmurt n Yahuda. D nețța i gezwaren alamma ț-țura.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen yeldi-d lḥekma di tmurt n Maṣer. Mi gțeddu yid-es yiwen uɛewdiw d azeggaɣ, yețmuqul amek ara yemmet.
Zzin-as-d leswaṛ ɛlayen yesɛan tiftilin, ț-țirgin iṛeqqen yellan deg umkan n tfeṛṛant ; di leɛwanseṛ n temdint-agi, ț-țamurt n Gumuṛ, iɛejmiyen ɣlayen n lyaman n mkul ṣṣenf akk-d ddheb,
Lɛahed-nni iwumi yețqeddim lewɛadi d iseflawen, daymi i s-ilaqen zzwaǧ, ula d nutni ad sɛunt lḥeṛma d warraw-nsent, ad țțaɣen awal iwakken ur qebblen ara ayen s wayes ara ččen.
A d-yekker yiwet n tɣuṛfeț am uḥeǧǧaǧu n tmes, armi d azeggaɣ amellal. Neɣ ilaq a t-id-yawi waḍu ɣerdaw n tegzirt n Kritus iwakken a ten-yekkes akk-d lexṛif.
Tawaɣit tamezwarut tɛedda. Mazal snat n twaɣyin nniḍen țeddunt-ed deffir-es, tefciwin-agi i d-yezwaren seg wass amezwaru armi d ass i deg yețwarfed ɣer igenni.
M'ara d-iṣuḍ waḍu seg usammer teqqaṛem ad iḥmu lḥal ; d ayen i d-ideṛṛun daɣen.
Ur țțarat ara țțaṛ, ur țarrat ara rregmat i wid i kkun-iregmen ; axaṭer ddɛut s lxiṛ i wiyaḍ axaṭer d annect-agi i gețṛaǧu deg-wen Sidi Ṛebbi.
Imi tmenɛeḍ leɛṭeṛ-nni, lmelk Lizyas akk-d Meryem-nni yellan d yemma-s n tezduɣt-nni, Meryem tella di leɛmeṛ akk-d Luṭs, aț-țxebbiṛen deg-s ṛebɛa iseggasen ; ț-țameṭṭut-nni tajdiṭ akk-d telt di lexluẓen ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail, aț-țekker ɣer Faris.
Mi d-ṣubben seg udrar, zzuɣṛen-d Sidna Ɛisa ɣer yiwen wergaz n temdint n Barya. Sekkren ccwal ger lɣaci ; aṭas n lɣaci iwumi qqaṛen d Sidna Ɛisa :
Yeskker-ed ger lɣaci, yeɣsa wayen i s-d-izzin i ugellid akk-d tagelda-inek iwakken ad iqleɛ iman-ik s tezmert n imawlan-ik akk-d warraw-nsen.
Yiwen uɛeskṛi yessenta yas isekkin deg idis, yesseɣlay-ed s tigzirt-nni. Yuɣal, yiwen lqebṭan ameqqran yeṭṭef amkan n lḥekma ɣer tama tayeffust n ugellid.
Ger widak-nni i d-yusan ad ɛeggden di temdint n Lquds, llan kra n iyunaniyen. Iɛuqeṛ-iten deg umenɣi n tmurt n Brisila, armi ț-țamurt n Amerkan iwakken ad amnen s Sidna Ɛisa.
Lameɛna nutni ad kemmlen abrid-nsen, ur țsetḥayen ara aț-țerrem taktabt-agi imermuct agi n lfeṭṭa, i tețțak-ed taxazabit n ddheb ɣef ddemma n txurtiwin ur tkeččuṛen ara ɣer daxel n limaren.
Lameɛna ur t-țțaǧan ara ad yefk izuṛan deg ulawen-nsen, ṭṭfen deg-s kra lweqt kan iwakken ad awḍen ɣer lefɛayel n wat Isṛail.
Asirem-agi d ayen yeṭṭfen tudert-nneɣ am umextaf ( tnejga ) yeṭṭfen lbabuṛ, yețɛedday akkin i leḥjab ɣer wemkan iqedsen,
Mbeɛd lweqt n usgiǧǧi ɣer tmurt n Yahuda. Qqim wis tnac, ɛeddin-d lweqt n twaɣit-nni, ɛeddan tilas deg wayen ɛeddan ɣer taggara. Deg ussan-nni, ɛeddan daɣen ṛbeɛṭac n leǧyal.
Mbeɛd lweqt n usgiǧǧi ɣer tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen yellan di temdint n Lquds, kunwi daɣen a d-texleq ddunit ; armi d ccetwa si zzman aneggaru, a t-id-yaweḍ wass wis xemsin.
Lefhama n bab igenwan uqbel kullec teṣfa, ț-țamhennit, ț-țuṛẓint, teččuṛ d leḥnana akk-d lecɣal yelhan, ur tesɛi timrurit ur tesɛi sin wudmawen.
Eɛni tixsi teswa akteṛ n wid ur neffiɣ ara ? Tawaɣit s tezmert n wawal-is, xedmet daɣen iberdan i gețțawin ɣer ccedda ț-țmusni n lǧameɛ iqedsen, ț-țin izmer a d-jehlen s tezmert n Sidi Ṛebbi ? Tazmert n Sidi Ṛebbi teɣleb leɛtab.
Imeslayen-agi « tikkelt nniḍen daɣen » sbeggnen-d belli ayen yețwaxelqen ad yenhezz ad yenger iwakken a d-yeqqim kan wayen yețdumun.
Tessexdam daɣen acḥal d abrid i t-qqnen s ixelxalen n ddunit, daymi i geggul abrid ajdid iwakken a d-yeqqim kan lewqam n lebḥeṛ yuɣal d iqelwacen.
Tajmaɛt-nni n umenɣi ɣef wayen yeɛnan izuṛan n lejdud-nneɣ, kkren-d iwakken ad amnen s webrid n Lmasiḥ, iwakken ad amnen.
Ini-yi-d daɣen i temḍelt-agi yellan di temdint n Ṛuma. Heggit iman-is d ameqqran ɣef wat Isṛail, d win akken i geṭṭfen lebni. Yețțubarek win i d-yusan s ṣṣifa n wemdan, i gxeddmen ayen yelhan, d nețța i gețuǧǧallen seg-s.
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq n temdint n Ṛuma, țțawin-d leḥyuḍ n wat Isṛail armi ț-țamurt n Arimati ; ma d wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, d wid iwumi i d-yessawel Sidi Ṛebbi aț-țesbedd lḥekma-s ; wid yesɛan lqima n lǧameɛ,
Barabas-agi yețwaḥbes ɣef ccwal i gexdem di ddunit meṛṛa ; akken kan i gețmeslay am temdint n Ifasus.
