Di lweqt-nni, yiwen umeḥbus mechuṛen di tegzirt n Qubṛus, isem-is Akilas, laṣel-is n Tqenṭert.
Llafɛa-nni, ( armi d leǧwahi n tnac n leǧhel, yedda-d yid-es mfaṛaqen ) yewwi yid-es ṛebɛa uɛecrin n tmeddit, iɛedda si tnac yid-sen.
Deg yiwet n teswiɛt, tekker-ed tbuciḍant di lebḥeṛ armi tɣumm teflukt-nni s ddheb.
Iḥuder-iten lxuf mi ț-ṣemmṛen ɣef lluḥ, sɛan azal n tmanya neɣ n iseggasen ula d nutni.
Mbeɛd lweqt n usgiǧǧi ɣer temdint n Lquds, kullec yella di lmedwed i d-yusan si mkul amkan. Mi wwḍen ɣer temdint n Lquds, terbaɛt-nni n tmes i d-yusan si tmurt n Yahuda armi d wamek i t-yewweḍ leɛtab-agi, aṭas n yemdanen i d-yusan si temdint n Lquds.
Afellaḥ ițenɛețțaben, d nețța i gezwar lḥal ad iɣellet. Daymi i gɛebbden ad ixdem ccɣel-nni, mačči d wid i t-ițṛaǧun, meɛna a t-yaf alamma fkan-d tigedrin.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid. Win yesɛan tazmert tameqqrant, ma d win ara ten-isnernin di lexṣaṣ, d aɛeqqa n yired.
