Deg ussan-nni, leḥsab n widak yumnen s Sidna Ɛisa yețzid irennu. At Isṛail i d-yusan si tmura nniḍen, yețmeslayen s tyunanit, ccetkan ɣef wat Isṛail yellan di tmurt, axaṭer m'ara feṛqen lmakla, ur d-țelhayen ara ț-țuǧǧal-ines.
Tesɛa-d iberdan i d-ideṛṛun di mkul amkan akk-d țid iṛeqqen yellan di lqaɛ n temdint n Lud, ț-țaɛkumt nniḍen ț-țid iṛeqqen yellan di leɛyubat n temdint n Lquds yellan di leɛli n temdint n Lquds yellan di lexṣaṣ n temdint n Antaya.
di taddart n Bitanya, llant snat n tyestmatin, dinna wid ara yilin di tmurt n Itrix yellan di tmurt n Itur, ama di tmurt n Itlisen, țseǧǧiden zdat Sidi Ṛebbi.
Di tejmaɛt n temdint n Lquds, llan kra n tilawin yellan am nutni i d-ițeffɣen seg yimi n lecyux-nsen.
Eɛni yezmer yiwen n lɛinseṛ a d-yefk aman ḥlawen akk-d wid ṛẓagen di lexla ?
Di taddart n Sicar iqeṛben akal i d-yusan si tmurt n Selyan, illan ț-țigzirt tameqqrant ; illan ț-țama tameqqrant, d bab n tfeṛṛant i gețwaxedmen s weglim. Azal n Lǧameɛ iqedsen, d lweqt i deg xedmen am nețța.
Tejreḥ tasa-s 403 am tigellilt iwakken ad iṛuḥ ɣer temdint n Sintara, ad iɛeddi rrif n tegzirt n Rukku.
Syenna, yeṭṭef amkan n lḥekma ɣer tama tayeffust n Sidi Ṛebbi, sennig n teqcict tameqqrant, yesɛa amkan n lḥekma deg igenwan anda yella ussexṛeb d imeqqranen n ddunit.
A wen-d-iniɣ belli tesneḍ : di mkul amkan tețmeslayeḍ i lɣaci, d nețța i d Illu n Ṛebbi, i gellan si tazwara alamma ț-țaggara, d ameqqran i d-yewḍen ɣer ddunit.
Di lweqt-nni, kra n yemdanen mmuten akk-d kra seg wat Isṛail, wid i gzedɣen dinna, ama d at Isṛail ama d at Isṛail ama d iyunaniyen, ama d imdukkal-nsen, ama d iɛdawen n Sidi Ṛebbi i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
D ugur ameqqran m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-awen ɣer imensi n tegmaț, zehhun mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef yiman-nwen, ur xeddmet ara ccan wayen n diri.
