Lameɛna aṭas n leṣnaf n tukciwin i d-ițasen si tmura nniḍen, țemyexdamen deffir-es, axaṭer akka ara yilin d imezwura.
Meɛna aṭas seg imiren i gesnum d lexṣaṣ n waman, ayagi meṛṛa țwaqehheṛ yerna ț-țamezduɣt n wafriwen,
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ. Meɛna di yal amkan tețțeddu-d deg webrid s tutlayin ur nețwassen ara, m'ara slen i wawal n Ṛebbi, m'ara țbecciṛen lexbaṛ n lxiṛ i wat Isṛail, ț-țțuǧǧal-nsen, ț-țuǧǧal-nsen, m'ara beccṛen, ad aruɣṛen fell-asen, ad ṛuḥen, ad beccṛen i wat Isṛail, ad ṛuḥen, ad beccṛen i wat Isṛail, wid yesɛan daɣen win ara beccṛen i wat Isṛail, wid yesɛan daɣen win ara d-sexḍuṛen ɣer temdinin, win ara d-yeḍsen, aț-țemmeslayen leǧnas nniḍen.
