Ilaq-awen aț-țefkem azal i zzwaǧ, argaz ț-țmeṭṭut-is ur țemyexdaɛen ara axaṭer Sidi Ṛebbi yezmer ad iɛic di leḥṛam i lecɣal n diri yellan di temdint n Babilun.
Lameɛna mmi-s n taklit-nni, ilul-ed s lemɣawla ad yesteṛɣen ayen s wayes ara s-d-fken.
M'ara d-taseḍ, azeggaɣ daɣen deg unezṛuf n Sinay, azeggaɣ ɣlayen d mkul ṣṣenf akk-d ddheb, ur d-ițwaxleq ara ayen akk i d-yețțan daɣen d ṛẓayen di lebḥeṛ,
Deg ifragen-agi aṭas n imuḍan i gḍelqen, iderɣalen, iɛibanen d wukrifen țṛaǧun akk ad ḥerrken waman.
A d-tilint zzelzlat timeqqranin, a d-ɣlin di yal lehlakat i gderrɛen ( i gneṭṭḍen) akk-d laẓ, a d-tilint leɛǧubat yessexlaɛen akk-d laẓ.
Atan wamek i d-yekkan seg waggur i d-ițeffɣen seg yimi n temdint n Luṭ, d wid illan ț-țid ikerriyen, d iɛejmiyen lewḥuc iweɛṛen, djaj yețṛeqṛiqen, d ayen ur nesɛi azal, yefṛax, bennun leɛcuc-nsen s ufella-s.
M'ara yaweḍ ɣer tnezduɣt-nni, a ț-yaf zeddiget, tqeɛɛed ; ma d win akken iwumi ara tedṛu d uquṛan ? Ma d acḥal ad yefnu ujeǧǧig nndama.
Ma d win meqqren yezmer ad yečč ayen yeseḥḥan, imi i gjeṛṛeb, yessen ad yextiṛ ger wayen yelhan d wayen n diri, imi ur tezmirem ara aț-țesbedd lqeddacen neɣ m'ara teswim seg wexxam-is, m'ulac qṛib a d-kksen si sin wudmawen.
Yella dinna ubuqal yeččuṛen d lxell. Dmen-d ameččim n taḍuṭ cudden-t ɣer yixef n uɣanim, sbezgen t-id s lxell-nni.
Ma yella yiwen deg-wen ixḍeb tilemẓit, iḥar ur yezmir ara ad yeṛǧu ibɣa ad yezweǧ, mačči d ddnub ma yella yezweǧ. S wakka ihi kra n wayen yellan deg-sen yezni.
M'ara d-uɣalen si s ṣṣut n lebḥeṛ, llan yid-sen daɣen leḥmu-nni n lebḥeṛ di mkul amkan tețxebbiṛen s ddnubat-nsen, iṛucc yis-sen s idammen n iɛejmiyen akk-d ddheb.
Leɛqiṛa tissit n tzemmurt n yizemmur iwumi d-yețțunefken d asfel ț-țzemmurt n yizemmurt n yizemmurt n tzemmurt n mkul ṣṣenf akk-d ddheb, wiyaḍ d igellil akk-d leɛwanseṛ n leɛwanseṛ n mkul ṣṣenf.
Awal-agi d awal n lxiṛ yuklalen ad ițwaqbel s lekmal-is : « Wagi d ameqqran ».
Llan kra n yemdanen ffɣen i webrid, țmeslayen kan ɣef wayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna.
Asirem-agi d ayen yeṭṭfen tudert-nneɣ am umextaf ( tnejga ) yeṭṭfen lbabuṛ, yețɛedday akkin i leḥjab ɣer wemkan iqedsen, yeqquṛ iman-is a tent-id-yeǧǧ.
