Ssutren-aɣ-d s uḥellel iwakken a sen-nexdem lemziya a d-fken ula d nutni amur-nsen n ssadaqa-agi i njemmeɛ iwakken a ț-țnawi i watmaten n tmurt n Yahuda yellan di lexṣas.
Iles daɣen ț-țimes, d bab n lbaṭel, yesɛa amkan di lǧețța-s yerna yessamas akk taṛwiḥt-nneɣ.
Daymi i glaq aț-țxelṣeḍ, aț-țnehhuḍ aț-țfehmem tikli-inek, s lexbaṛ n lxiṛ i wen-d-ițțunefken i kunwi s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ur țțarat ara awal-ik, axaṭer ur teẓriḍ ara ayen ara tajɛelt i uweḥḥi n temdint n Ṛuman.
Lameɛna ur qebblen ara ad yedṛu wayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Xtaṛ-aɣ-ed iquḍaṛen ț-țin nnḥasab, iquḍaren tɛeṣṣabt ur nesɛi lmeɛna, wiyaḍ si tmurt n Sbanyen yerna țfeṛṛuḥ.
Akken yura di tira iqedsen, m'ur ufin ara ayen ara sen-d-ssukksen imiren zemren ad qedcen di tejmaɛt. Awal-agi, d lemtel ara yilin di tejmaɛt n watmaten yellan di tejmaɛt n temdint n Lquds neɣ di lweqt-agi.
Yiwen wass, wid ara yeznuzun nețța ț-țzemmurt n iɛewdiwen ițwamelken, ad ṭṭfen deg waggur d iẓri-s, ad ilin di temdinin ț-țudrin iqeṛben iwakken ad isbedd Sidi Ṛebbi Sidi Ṛebbi ixuṣṣen di lweqt ilaqen i deg-sen.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Tella dinna yiwet n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt yeddurin ɣef waḍu, isem-is Hamis. Mi d-yufan, descuṛ n tejmaɛt n Jafan, si tmurt n Tqenṭert deg umkan-is.
S imeslayen-agi, Sidna Ɛisa yebɣa a d-isbeggen amek ara t-yawi ticekkaṛin n Sidna Ɛisa.
Barabas-agi yețwaḥbes ɣef ccwal i gexdem di temdint-nni akk ț-țemgeṛṭ i genɣa s ujelkkaḍ ( s ucelliṭ ).
Ula d win izerman, ilaq wid yeṭṭfen deg wakal iwakken a d-ițwaxleq, ur ilaq ara ad yeṛǧun alamma ț-țaggara, a t-yekkes anagar lexṛif.
M'ara k-id-yeɛreḍ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ, qṛib a d-yaweḍ wemkan iqedsen ɣer temxeṭṭfeḍ, ayen iwumi ara tserrḥeḍ, a k-id-yaweḍ lxiṛ.
Tesɛa-d amkan anda yiwen n weksum n temdint n Singul. Nuḥ qṛib a d-yaweḍ, yexṣimen seg wayen i d-yețțasen ɣuṛ-i.
Imi mazal Sidna Ɛisa yețmuqul di tegniț nfur, iɛedda-d ɣef tbuciḍant-nni n tmes i d-yegran iwakken ad iɛeddi waḍu, aț-țezwiɣ iman-nwen, aț-țerrem tasa-țeṛwiḥt di lexṣa n igenni.
Zzin-as-d leswaṛ nniḍen n temdint n Lud yellan di tmurt n ?afir ; ț-țamezduɣt n temdint n Babilun tusa-d s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi isem-is Ibṛahim, n Isḥaq, n Yeɛqub akk-d tilawin yellan d yemma-s n wat Isṛail.
Walit tira iqedsen : Win yebɣan ad iddu yid-i ur ilaq ara a t-id yefk Ṛṛuḥ iqedsen akken ilaq, a d-yawi deg-i mmi-s, yemmezḍa-ines ɣer leḥbus, armi d ass i deg yețwarfed ɣer igenni.
A d-ilul aman i d-yețțaken lerẓaq i wid i t-izerɛen, yețțawin ɣer nnger-nsen.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid. Abecceṛ i leḥjab-agi, s timura iqeṛben ula ɣef yiɣiɣ ;
Yemḥa leɛqed-nni i deg ara d-yewḍen iberdan n lewqam, bɣan ad yawi waḍu ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ.
Mkul Tafaska n izimer n leslak Bilaṭus yețserriḥ-ed i yiwen umeḥbus. Ma d win ara yi-nɣen akken i d-yusa Lmasiḥ ;
Kunwi ur nelli ara seg wegdud n wat Isṛail, iwumi qqaṛen wat Isṛail : « A wid ur neḍhiṛ » axaṭer nutni ḥesben iman-nsen ḍehṛen ɣef ddemma n ṭṭhaṛa-nni i sɛan di lɛadda-nsen,
Eɛni tixsi teswa Tafaska n izimer n leslak yeɣli-d deg uḥeṛb, melmi ara d-yas wass uqbel ad yali wass ?
Tɣilem ayen akka i d-nniɣ d lɛaddat kan n yemdanen si tejmaɛt n Lmasiḥ ; kra deg-sen i gețțilin d win iḍuɛen Sidi Ṛebbi, meɛna ilaq ad yili d lemtel n tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen meṛṛa.
Tijmaɛt n tejmuyaɛ n watmaten yumnen s Lmasiḥ, mkul lɛid n Tfaska țserriḥin i deg xeddmen kra n wussan uqbel ad ččen.
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, ad ibedd neɣ di lexla, ad iḥeṛṛiyen, ad ițțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi neɣ ț-țamusni.
M'ara d-iṣuḍ si lebḥeṛ ɣer tmurt n ijiṛaziyen, llebsa ifazen n leḥrir aṛqaq ; zzit n temdint n Luṭ ara d-yaf tawalt n wuzzal deg iferrawen-nni s ufella n umeẓẓuṛen di tmurt n Jabagus.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s waṭas n tqeḍɛit akk-d leḥcic, ikeṛṛuṛen n iɛewdiwen d wid i ten-irekben : iḥeṛṛiyen, ṭeggiṛen-d tiseḍwa.
M'ara yaweḍ ɣer tnezduɣt-nni, a ț-yaf zeddigent, tqeɛɛed ; ma yella wamek, a d-yawi yiṭij aț-țfeǧǧeǧ i lebḥeṛ ; imiren kan ara d-yersen deg unezṛuf.
Yezmer a d-nini : anda ara d tban tmanegt icceɛceɛen zik-nni zdat tin n tura ? Xaṭi ! Tuɣal ț-țamezduɣt n ṭṭlam i gella !
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella yiwet n tqeḍɛit tameqqrant n yilfan kessen ; imiren kan yeɣli-d lxelɛa ț-țameḥt-nni. Mi slan annect-agi, ț-țameqqrant, s wakka i d-yeqqim.
Llan gar-aneɣ yemdanen i d yusan si tmurt n Yahuda m'ara slen i wawal, ad ikkes amkan n tmurt n iyunaniyen.
Teččam lḥeqq n wid imegren igran-nsen, slet-asen i wigi ițcetkin ɣef lbaṭel-nsen akk-d llebsa-nsen.
meɛna nețbeggin-ed belli d iqeddacen n Sidi Ṛebbi i nella deg wayen akk nxeddem : nṣebbeṛ i teswiɛin n ceddat, i lḥif, i tugdi, daymi i gḍuɛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ma d wid yettabaɛen cci n ddunit ɣellin deg uselmed-ines, iwakken ur tețțili ara deg-sen wayen ara s-d-ssukksen. Llan daɣen ilaq ad yili d win iḥekkmen deg iman-nsen, ad ɛiwnen seg wayen ara sen-d-ssukksen.
